<br>
I'd like to hear from all folks.<br>
<br>
I've dragged a few corpses from some sticky spots and only once received a donation of 10pp in CC (I've never asked because I've wanted to see the result). I've done so while sneak/hiding along with some minimal risk (mobs <!--EZCODE UNDERLINE START--><u>do</u><!--EZCODE UNDERLINE END--> have a chance to see through), and it's *very* slow (for the record). <br>
<br>
I've got colleagues who receive tells from other zones asking them to come pick suchandsuch a lock, or to drag from suchandsuch a deathtrap.  I currently get tells asking me to fetch corpses from the bottom of Befallen (no risk, but inconvenient).<br>
<br>
What do people normally pay for these *other* tasks? If a rez is worth 100pp, what's it worth to be able to get that corpse to you for the rez? .. and from behind that locked door?<br>
<br>
What other classes get asked to do things under this umbrella? How much do you tip the bard for pointing you in your corpse's direction?<br>
<br>
Please note that this is not a b*tch session. I'd just like to hear more on this subject. <p><a href="http://eq.castersrealm.com/players/view_profile.asp?Id=74102"><b><font face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif">Lannella 
