I'll always look for a bard first when I've needed to locate a corpse, knowing that the necro will have other chances later.  I've maxed up Bind Wounds and never ask for heals (though when a healer sees you taking the initiative of bandaging I often get one anyway).  I am guilty of asking for the rare sow on a corpse run, but never when I've died by my own foolishness (penance).<br>
